Instalación de Docker:
1. sudo apt update 
2. sudo apt install apt-transport-https ca-certificates curl software-properties-common -y
3. curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo apt-key add
4. sudo add-apt-repository "deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu focal stable"
5. sudo apt update
6. sudo apt install -y docker-ce docker-ce-cli
7. sudo systemctl status docker
8. sudo usermod -aG docker ${USER}
9. su - ${USER}
10. id -nG

Verificar el correcto funcionamiento de Docker:

11. docker run hello-world

Creación de un Dockerfile: 
12. docker build -t mydocker-01 .
13. docker run -d -p 8080:80 --name so-demo mydocker-01
14. docker images -a 

Abrir un puerto para un contenedor de Docker: 

sudo docker run -d -p 8081:80 --name sistoper -v $(pwd):/usr/local/apache2/htdocs httpd

docker ps
